    <summary>Terminal activity time-machine and developer productivity tracker</summary>
    <description>
OpsTrail is a local-first, privacy-focused terminal activity tracker that records everything you do in your shell.

Features:
- Automatic activity tracking (commands, directories, sessions)
- Time travel navigation - jump back to where you were working
- Search through your terminal history
- Analytics and statistics about your work patterns
- Session management with idle detection
- Project awareness via projwarp integration
- Context notes for leaving breadcrumbs
- PowerShell integration included

Track your terminal activity, search your history, and boost your productivity with OpsTrail.
